[[unpartei/LinkLanguage|LinkLanguage]][[http://google.com/search?q=LinkLanguage| °]] as used in [[unpartei/WiKi|WiKi]][[http://google.com/search?q=WiKi|➜°]]s allows [[unpartei/CollectiveThinking|CollectiveThinking]][[http://google.com/search?q=CollectiveThinking|➜°]] and [[unpartei/CollectiveWork|CollectiveWork]][[http://google.com/search?q=CollectiveWork|➜°]] ing to an arbitrary degree of detail.

Besides that it makes [[unpartei/ReFactoring|ReFactoring]][[http://google.com/search?q=ReFactoring|➜°]] of a page easier, because bigger chunks of text can be [[unpartei/FactoredOut|FactoredOut]][[http://google.com/search?q=FactoredOut|➜°]] to a separate page.

